description:
Trendy West side studio located in the heart of Harlem! Apt located one block away from all major public transportation. A, B, C,D, & 1 trains & buses. Studio located walking distance to Apollo Theatre, Magic Johnson Movie Theatre, various bars/clubs/restaurants, supermarkets, library, retail stores, historical churches and more!

Fourth Floor Walk Up Studio Apt. NO ELEVATOR!! Listing is for entire apartment. One Queen Sized bed, a couch, and twin sized bed.

Guest can access laundry room for an additional fee and provide own soap.

I will be at the apartment when you arrive to give you keys, information and introduction of the neighborhood. I am available via phone call and text 24/7. If I am needed in person that can be arranged as well.

Neighborhood is located in the upper west side of Harlem. 1 block away from A, B, C, D & 1 trains. Also 1 block away from many bus stops including M60 which drops you off at LaGuardia Airport. I live right next door to a supermarket and many sit-in, fast food, social eateries.

One block away from ALL major MTA trains & buses

Please no smoking inside the apt.

hosts.about: I love reading, writing, music, shopping and riding my bike. I have an obsession with watching foreign films and I have a variety of lipsticks and eyelashes lol. My favorite seasons are spring and fall because everyone is outdoors having fun! I love traveling and visiting Jamaica is my top five! I love meeting new people and learning fun facts. I can tell you all the great inexpensive places to visit in NYC!!
